title: Space Quest Collection ( All 6 Games, 1 Remake, And A Launcher)
description:
Space Quest Collection by Sierra On-line

Space Quest 1: The Sarien Encounter (VGA)
Space Quest 2: Vohaul's Revenge (CGA)
Space Quest 2: Vohaul's Revenge (VGA Style Remake by Infamous Adventures)
Space Quest 3: The Pirates Of Pestultion (EGA)
Space Quest 4: The Time Rippers (VGA)
Space Quest 5: The Next Mutation (VGA)
Space Quest 6: The Spinal Frontier

No Need to install
Just run the included Sierra Launcher
Pick the game you want to play and it will either boot up DOSBOX ( Included) or just load the game Natively.

Enjoy

     Billetwound
